name: NBI Sustainable Canadian Short Term Bond ETF
longDescription: The NBI Sustainable Canadian Short Term Bond ETF's investment objective is to provide a steady flow of income with an emphasis on capital preservation while focusing on debt instruments designed to raise funds that promote a positive environmental and or social impact and or contribute to sustainable development.
